data.title: Not Wowed at all
data.text: Visiting Calif. and my brother says lets try Rubios.  Concept is very good but concept is only as good as the people implementing.  When we received our food (I ordered two classic tacos with rice & beans) my shells were cold with a touch of warmth.  There wasn't much steak in tacos and with the cool shells not a very good first impression for a new customer.  The black beans were very good although small portion.  Rice was ok.  I think had the taco been better I would have liked the overall taste.  As it is there are too many places to eat and not enough time so I would not return here.

data.title: Beyond reproach
data.text: I normally do not write reviews of any fast food restaurant but the nice service at this one deserves to be praised. Food was delicious and the staff was very friendly. The best Rubio I have ever visited.
